Generic single-database configuration for MCP Analytics.

## Usage

### Create a new migration

```bash
# Auto-generate migration from model changes
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Add new column"

# Create empty migration
alembic revision -m "Custom migration"
```

### Apply migrations

```bash
# Upgrade to latest
alembic upgrade head

# Upgrade one version
alembic upgrade +1

# Downgrade one version
alembic downgrade -1

# Show current version
alembic current

# Show migration history
alembic history
```

### Environment Variables

Set `ANALYTICS_DATABASE_URL` to override the database URL in alembic.ini:

```bash
export ANALYTICS_DATABASE_URL="postgresql+asyncpg://user:pass@localhost/analytics"
alembic upgrade head
```
